  &lt;ul&gt; 
   &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-cloud/spring-cloud-contract/pull/684&quot; class=&quot;external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;修复了解析基于YAML合约的顺序错误问题&lt;/a&gt;，现在将首先读取自定义解析器。&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; 
   &lt;li&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/spring-cloud/spring-cloud-contract/issues?q=is%3Aclosed+milestone%3A2.0.1.RELEASE&quot; class=&quot;external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;缺陷修复&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/li&gt; 
